history.content:
Want to have your voice heard by EECS faculty, staff, and the Chairs? The EECS department welcomes you to fill out the EECS Undergraduate Survey here:

 

https://berkeley.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_8qRSeLV6VdWeKWx

 

The EECS Department and HKN have created the 2018-19 EECS Undergraduate Survey so you can provide input and feedback. This is a great opportunity for you to make a real impact in your classes, student life, and campus culture. Your thoughts will reach faculty and staff and will be used to help improve the department and the community!

 

In addition, once you complete the survey, you can choose to enter a prize drawing to win one of fifteen (15) $10 Amazon gift cards! Just make sure to fill out the form at the end of the survey.

 

Your response is completely anonymous. We encourage you to respond openly and honestly!
history.subject: Please Complete the EECS Undergraduate Survey
